        "text_KpKYXM": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>To deliver greater speed and tighter quality control, we brought the process in-house, investing in our own inventory and printing technology and taking ownership from start to finish. The impact was immediate; standard turnaround times dropped from over a month to just five days. Today, we’ve gone even further, offering 24-hour rush services on popular products, with capabilities expanding every day to meet the needs of our customers without compromising quality.</p>",
